{"tid":693092,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG]動漫台緣份扭蛋機計劃","createTime":"2018-06-07T07:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T05:15:08.000Z","uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff4f7705e7b340e254342a0c15617d7316b9264","tid":693092,"uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/692372/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/692372/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，緣於小弟琴晚開呢個post，短短一晚大概已經收集左20份問卷，有男有女，比例大概係7:3。<br />\n<br />\n由於反應踴躍，所以小弟想係旺角區整返部屬於大家既緣份扭蛋機，地點應該會係信和中心入面既店鋪，比返動漫愛好者一個交友機會，歡迎大家提出唔同既意見/狠評，再睇下點實行，感謝各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問卷調查Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fe6Plh03iiQCCX5p73&d=PnqHV%2BUNtOls%2FEpEQrMap9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=98039aa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73</a><br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n好宅之人 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fveryotaku&d=PnqHV%2BUNtOls%2FEpEQrMap9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bc60b787\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku</a><br />\n緣份配對計劃 <a href=\"https://matchup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatchup.hk&d=PnqHV%2BUNtOls%2FEpEQrMap9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c060c91b\" target=\"_blank\">https://matchup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"fa9dc23339321c0dc99336ef743442594b347fcd","tid":693092,"uid":178819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b5b9e38597fbdbab29d1a28f3b96e039719415c","tid":693092,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"龜sir整份配對問卷出黎"},{"pid":"d4e97c9c092f64cffa929c832be04b4cc3f7a3e2","tid":693092,"uid":178819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":